-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Shaw Communications, Empire Company, Perpetual Energy 
-- 
-- Fri Jun 27, 2014 07:19AM EDT
-- None



June 27 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Empire Company Ltd and Perpetual Energy, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Shaw Communications <SJRb.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises to hold from sell * Empire Company Ltd <EMPa.TO>: CIBC raises to sector outperformer from sector performer * Tahoe Resources Inc <THO.TO>: Raymond James cuts to market perform from outperform * Perpetual Energy <PMT.TO>: CIBC, RBC upgrade the stock  Following is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. * Belo Sun Mining <BSX.TO>: Dundee Capital cuts target to C$0.50 from C$0.75; rating buy * DragonWave Inc <DWI.TO>: CIBC ups to sector outperformer -spec. from sector underperformer * DragonWave Inc <DWI.TO>: CIBC raises target price to C$3 from C$1 * Empire Company Ltd <EMPa.TO>: CIBC raises to sector outperformer from sector performer * Empire Company Ltd <EMPa.TO>: CIBC raises target price to C$82 from C$80 * Empire Company Ltd <EMPa.TO>: NBF raises target to C$74 from C$73; rating sector perform * Etrion <ETX.TO>: Paradigm cuts target price to C$0.80 from C$1; rating buy * Fortuna Silver Mines Inc <FVI.TO>: Raymond James cuts to outperform from strong buy * Fortuna Silver Mines Inc <FVI.TO>: Raymond James raises target price to C$6.50 from C$6 * Lumenpulse Inc <LMP.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target to C$29 from C$25; rating buy * Lumenpulse Inc <LMP.TO>: NBF raises target price to C$28 from C$24; rating outperform * Lumenpulse Inc <LMP.TO>: Raymond James raises target to C$26 from C$25; rating outperform * Mosaic Capital Corp <M.V>: Raymond James raises target to C$14.75 from C$13.75; outperform * Pacific Rubiales Energy <PRE.TO>: Barclays starts with overweight; target price of C$26.80 * Paramount Resources Ltd <POU.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target to C$75 from C$70; buy * Perpetual Energy <PMT.TO>: CIBC raises to sector outperformer -spec. from sector performer * Perpetual Energy <PMT.TO>: CIBC raises target price to C$2.35 from C$2 * Perpetual Energy <PMT.TO>: RBC raises to outperform from sector perform * Perpetual Energy <PMT.TO>: RBC raises price target to C$2.50 from C$2  * Shaw Communications <SJRb.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises to hold from sell * Shaw Communications <SJRb.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises price target to C$26 from C$24 * Shaw Communications <SJRb.TO>: NBF raises target to C$25.50 from C$24.50; underperform * Shaw Communications <SJRb.TO>: RBC raises target to C$26 from C$25; rating sector perform